race.comment: EXCAPING THE BLUES (3) is racing with great purpose and has four wins on end, most recently getting home by 0.8 lengths over 1509m at Listed level at this track (Turf). Inosencio Diego has been the pilot at his last four wins. Among the leading chances. SONIC POSSE (1) started at $3.40 last time but could only manage fifth, beaten 4 lengths, at this track over 1509m. Sound record at this distance with three wins and two minor placings from five runs and is among the leading chances. SALINE RIVER (5) was returning from a break last time out and proved too classy, scoring by 2.5 lengths over 1509m at this track (Turf). Has a strong second-up record and looks a big threat to the top selection. AARON (7) settled well back before finishing 7 lengths adrift in sixth over 1509m at this track (Turf) last time. Should park just off the speed. Deserves respect on best figures. Something for the Multiples: COASTAL BRINK (4)
